Bartell LaRue https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bartell_LaRue 0 Jimmie Bartell LaRue (1932 – 5 January 1990) was an American voice actor who performed on many US television shows including Star Trek, Mission: Impossible, The Brady Bunch (Episode 41), and Mannix. LaRue wrote, directed and produced the film Satan War (1979).
